{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 23,
  "title": "第二十三章（同道）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "希言自然。飄風不終朝。暴雨不終日。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰為此，天地而弗能久。又況於人乎？"
    },
    {
      "text": "故從事而道者，同於道。德者，同於德。失者，同於失。"
    },
    {
      "text": "同於德者，道亦德之。同於失者，道亦失之。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "希言者，謂愛言也。愛言者，自然之道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "飄風，疾風也。驟雨，暴雨也。言疾不能長，暴不能久也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孰，誰也。誰為此飄風暴雨者乎？天地所為。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不能終於朝暮也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地至神合為飄風暴雨，尚不能使終朝至暮，何況人欲為暴卒乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從，為也。人為事當如道安靜，不當如飄風驟雨也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 3,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道者，謂好道人也。同於道者，所謂與道同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "德者，謂好德之人也。同於德者，所謂與德同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "失，謂任己而失人也。同於失者，所謂與失同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與道同者，道亦樂得之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與德同者，德亦樂得之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與失同者，失亦樂失之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "君信不足於下，下則應君以不信也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此言物類相歸，同聲相應，同氣相求。雲從龍，風從虎，水流濕，火就燥，自然之類也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聽之不聞名曰希，下章言，道之出言淡兮其無味也，視之不足見，聽之不足聞，然則無味不足聽之言，乃是自然之至言也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言暴疾美興不長也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 25,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "從事，謂舉動，從事於道者也。道以無形無為成濟萬物，故從事於道者，以無為為君，不言為教，緜緜若存而物得其真，與道同體，故曰同於道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "得，少也，少則得，故曰得也。行得則與得同體，故曰，同於得也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "失，累多也，累多則失，故曰失也。行失則與失同體，故曰，同於失也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言隨行其所，故同而應之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "忠信不足於下，焉有不信焉。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
